text: Jean-Jacques Guillet (born 16 October 1946) is a French politician. He is mayor of Chaville. He was the deputy for Hauts-de-Seine's 8th constituency in the National Assembly of France from 1993 to 2017, as a member of Rally for the Republic, Rally for France and then The Republicans.
